title: Beyond Basic Yoga for Dummies with Sara Ivanhoe x264 aac [MP4]

Move beyond basic yoga with 12 new postures. This unintimidating program steps up the physical challenge of yoga to enhance your yoga practice. If you loved Basic Yoga Workout For Dummies, then you re ready to enhance your yoga practice by delving deeper into other important aspects of yoga. Beyond Basic Yoga For Dummies builds on the foundation you started in Basic Yoga Workout For Dummies and guides you through 12 more postures that pick up the pace.
